      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: Order of the Mutant</em></p><p>As a bonus action, you mark a creature that you can see within 30 feet of you. Until the end of your next turn, the suffer one of the side effects from one of your active Mutagens that you are not ignoring with your Strange Metabolism.<br /><br /><strong>Amplify</strong>. This curse lasts up to 1 minute. Starting after the end of your next turn, the cursed creature can make a Constitution saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the curse on itself on a success.</p>",
